---
import LayoutWithoutSidebar from "@/layouts/LayoutWithoutSideBar.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<LayoutWithoutSidebar>

<div class="card-base glass-card relative w-full mx-auto my-8 py-12 px-10 text-center">
    <div class="
        text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100 text-[0.9rem] bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.05)]
        dark:bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.05)] rounded-full mb-[1.8rem] py-[0.4rem] px-[1.2rem]
        border-[0.5px] border-indigo-300/40 w-fit justify-center items-center inline-flex
    ">
        <span class="text-[1.2rem] drop-shadow-[0_0_3px_#a78bfa]">🛸</span> 
        导航信号中断 · 坐标漂移 
        <span class="text-[1.2rem] drop-shadow-[0_0_3px_#a78bfa]">🌌</span>
    </div>

    <div class="error-code">404</div>

    <div class="glow-text text-[2.3rem] font-[600] text-[var(--primary)]">
        ✦ 跃迁失败 ✦
    </div>

    <div class="
        text-[1.05rem] leading-[1.6] text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100
        mt-[1.2rem] mb-[2rem] py-[0] px-[1rem] mw-[550px] ml-auto mr-auto
    ">
        哎呀，看起来您探索的页面已经消失在星际迷雾中，可能被外星人捕获，或是被流星雨带走了。
        <br>
        不如返回地球基地，重新校准导航？
    </div>

    <!-- 按钮: 返回首页/返回上一页 -->
    <div class="
        flex wrap gap-[1.2rem] justify-center mt-[1.2rem] mb-[1rem]
    ">
        <a class="btn404
            text-neutral-100 dark:text-neutral-100
            bg-[linear-gradient(105deg,_#3b49df,_#6366f1)]
            hover:bg-[linear-gradient(105deg,_#4f5cf0,_#7c3aed)]
        " id="homeBtn" href="/">
            <Icon name="fa6-solid:house"/> 
            <span>返回首页</span>
        </a>
        <button class="btn404 btn-back-home
                text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100
        " id="goBackBtn">
            <Icon name="fa6-solid:arrow-left"/> 
            <span>返回上一页</span>
        </button>
    </div>
</div>
    
</LayoutWithoutSidebar>

<script>
    (function() {
        
        // 返回上一页功能
        const backBtn = document.getElementById('goBackBtn');
        console.log("script loaded");
        if (backBtn) {
            backBtn.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                e.preventDefault();
                if (window.history.length > 1) {
                    window.history.back();
                } else {
                    // 如果没有历史记录, 跳转至首页
                    window.location.href = '/';
                }
            });
        }

        // 加载完后的背景动画
        const styleBreathing = document.createElement('style');
        styleBreathing.textContent = `
            @keyframes gentlePulse {
                0% { backdrop-filter: blur(12px); }
                100% { backdrop-filter: blur(14px); }
            }
            .glass-card {
                animation: glassFadeIn 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.9, 0.4, 1.1);
            }
            @keyframes glassFadeIn {
                0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px) scale(0.96); }
                100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0px) scale(1); }
            }
        `;
        document.head.appendChild(styleBreathing);

        // 埋一个小彩蛋😜
        console.log("%c✨ 404 探索者，欢迎来到星际边界 ✨", "color: #a5f3fc; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;");
        console.log("%c您寻找的页面可能正在外太空漫游，点击导航返回家园吧~", "color: #cbd5e6; font-size: 12px;");
    }) ();
</script>

<style>
    .btn404 {
        @apply inline-flex items-center 
            gap-[0.6rem] py-[0.9rem] px-[2rem]
            rounded-full border-[1.5px] border-indigo-300/40
            font-[900] shadow-[0_8px_18px_-8px_rgba(59,73,223,0.4)]
            hover:shadow-[0_15px_25px_-10px_rgba(99,102,241,0.5)];
        
        transition: all 0.25s ease;
    }

    .btn404:hover{
        transform: translateY(-3px);
    }

    .glass-card {
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .glass-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .error-code {
        font-size: clamp(6rem, 20vw, 12rem);
        font-weight: 900;
        line-height: 1;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #60a5fa, #a78bfa, #4ade80, #22d3ee);
        background-size: 300% 300%;
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        background-clip: text;
        color: transparent;
        animation: gradientShift 8s ease infinite, levitate 5s ease-in-out infinite;
        text-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        font-family: 'Consolas', monospace;
    }

    @keyframes gradientShift {
        0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
        100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    }

    @keyframes levitate {
        0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
        50% { transform: translateY(-8px); }
        100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
    }
</style>
